    "Devlin et al. (2019) introduced BERT, an innovative architecture that allows the pre-training of deep bidirectional transformers, and since then, several BERT-variant models have been developed, such as RoBERTa (Liu et al., 2019) and ALBERT (Lan et al., 2020)."
